<aura:documentation>
	<aura:description>
        <p>A <code>ui_popover:popover</code> component that displays a popover (tooltip).</p>
<pre>&lt;ui_popover:popover&gt;
    &lt;aura:set attribute="popoverBody"&gt;
        - popover body goes here -
    &lt;/aura:set&gt;
    - content triggering popover goes here -
&lt;/ui_popover:popover&gt;</pre>
        
        <h4>Sample code</h4>
        <p>The following example displays a popover when the user hovers on a link placed in a sentence.</p>
<pre>&lt;div&gt;Note that&amp;amp;nbsp;
&lt;ui_popover:popover&gt;
    &lt;aura:set attribute="popoverBody"&gt;
        &lt;h3 class="slds-section-title"&gt;The Popover Title&lt;/h3&gt;
        &lt;p class="slds-m-bottom--x-small"&gt;Some textual description or any kind of markup including other components.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/aura:set&gt;
    &lt;a href="javascript:void(0);"&gt;hovering over this content (not necessarily a link) triggers the popover&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/ui_popover:popover&gt;
&amp;amp;nbsp;and it renders really nicely with SLDS.&lt;/div&gt;</pre>
        
    </aura:description>
</aura:documentation>